Peter A. Bordes, Jr.

Public asset : 5,352,486 USDLinked companies :  Beasley Broadcast Group Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Peter A. Bordes, Jr., is Executive Chairman at oneQube, Inc.He is on the Board of Directors at Beasley Broadcast Group, Inc. Mr. Bordes was previously employed as Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by M.T. Performance Marketing, Inc, Chairman by Empire Media, Inc., a Principal by Greater Media, Inc., a Principal by NinthDecimal, Inc., and a Principal by Roomlinx, Inc.He also served on the board at Conservation International Foundation.



