About Peter Borders, Jr.


Peter, Jr. married at 3 times, each one in Sumner Co., TN. Peter, Jr.. & Catherine (Dowel) Borders,  were married in 1844 in Sumner Co., TN. Dates of marriage to his 1st & 3rd wives unknown to me at this time.
He can be located on the 1830 census for Allen Co., KY , pg. 56, with 2 M under age 5, 1 M age 20-29, 1 F under age 5, 1 F age 5-10, 1 F 20-29.
The DAR file of Peter Borders (1756 - 1837) gives alternate death location for Peter Borders, Jr. as Sumner Co., TN. .






